data.description: This home's got it all! Enjoy a fresh kitchen with brand-new appliances and soak in the natural light from the updated windows. Slide open the new door to your partially covered deck – the ideal spot for your morning coffee. Stay comfy year-round with updated electrical and a modern AC unit. The finished basement adds a bonus hangout space with an updated bathroom. Outside, there's a refreshing 5ft pool to splash in, and your two-car garage is heated – no more chilly mornings. Casual living with a touch of flair – welcome home!
